<varlistentry id="options.SaveWorkspace">
	<term>SaveWorkspace <emphasis remap='I'>"name" file_name</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Write list of presently running applications with its position
                and desktop number into specified file. You can run this file
                at a later time as a shell script to restore state of the
                desktop. Note this does not work for many applications that
                does not provide needed ICCCM properties on its windows.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
